<!--
    Default (English) strings. Add a values-XX/strings.xml sibling for each
    locale you want to support — Compose Multiplatform picks the closest
    match based on the user's system locale at runtime.

    All UI text must live here. Replace any `Text("…")` literal with
    `Text(stringResource(Res.string.…))`. Generated accessor lives in
    com.adsamcik.temperaturedashboard.core.ui.resources.Res.
-->
